248
00:11:00,500 --> 00:11:02,900
( Telephone rings )

249
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:04,400
( Ring )

250
00:11:04,430 --> 00:11:06,600
Josuke: Shit! No answer.
This is bad!

251
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,800
Koichi: He must have left then,

252
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,640
which means they
probably baited jotaro

253
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:11,270
to go and meet them somewhere.

254
00:11:11,310 --> 00:11:14,410
Josuke: Damn! All we can do now
is go after the copy.

255
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,780
Koichi: What do we do?

256
00:11:15,810 --> 00:11:17,780
I couldn’t tell you two apart
to save my life!

257
00:11:17,810 --> 00:11:20,420
Josuke: Yeah. Stealing my face
is weird enough,

258
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:23,320
but what really
freaks me out are his fingers.

259
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,860
How often do you catch
a glimpse of your fingers

260
00:11:25,890 --> 00:11:27,660
compared to your face?

261
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:31,630
I realized that stand had copied
me down to the fingerprints.

262
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:34,530
Tamami: Huh? Hey, josuke,

263
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,660
you’re back early.

264
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:37,670
Where’s master koichi?

265
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:40,670
H-hazamada? What the heck
are you doing here?

266
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:44,440
Hazamada: Tamami kobayashi, huh?
( Chuckles )

267
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:46,940
Show off: You have no idea
why we’re hanging out?

268
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:48,840
Come on. Give it a guess.

269
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,780
Tamami: I’m all guessed out.

270
00:11:50,810 --> 00:11:53,580
Show off: So you don’t even
have one little theory?

271
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:56,050
Tamami: Nuh-uh.
Should I have one, sir?

272
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,820
Show off: Nah, you’re good.

273
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,760
Jotaro: Step on it.

274
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:11,600
Josuke: If we don’t hurry
and catch up with hazamada,

275
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:13,500
jotaro is done for!

276
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:18,570
♪

277
00:12:18,610 --> 00:12:21,210
Koichi: We can’t let jotaro
meet up with the copy,

278
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,780
or it’ll be a total disaster.

279
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:25,550
Josuke: Yeah, but I haven’t
figured out a solution yet,

280
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:28,320
so for now,
all we can do is run.

281
00:12:31,020 --> 00:12:32,950
( Tamami groans )

282
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:36,760
Girl: We’ll catch you later,
josuke!

283
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:38,990
- Girl #2: See you tomorrow!
- Girl #3: Yeah, take it easy!

284
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,000
( Hazamada grumbling )

285
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,730
Girl #4: See you, josuke!

286
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:44,470
Girl #5: Bye, josuke.
Have a good evening.

287
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,600
Hazamada: Why the hell are
these chattering schoolgirls

288
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:47,970
only saying goodbye to you?

289
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,870
