like that to me

290
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:51,610
when I leave school for the day.

291
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:53,840
( Groans )
But why should I care,

292
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:56,210
since every girl in this school
is butt ugly.

293
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:58,650
- Girl #6: Josuke...
- Show off: Eh?

294
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,750
Girl #6: Um,
could you read this?

295
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:02,850
( Hazamada groans )

296
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:04,950
Girl #6: Well, bye then.

297
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:07,660
Hazamada: Why are you
accepting notes from her?

298
00:13:07,690 --> 00:13:09,460
Like it would do you any good.

299
00:13:09,490 --> 00:13:11,460
( Growls ) God damn it.

300
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:14,330
What the hell makes a jerk
like you so special anyway?!

301
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,930
Show off: What’s your deal?

302
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,870
The show’s over now,
so let’s just move on.

303
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:19,240
Hazamada: Wha...

304
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,470
Show off:
Maybe you’ve forgotten,

305
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,800
but we don’t have time
to dillydally.

306
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,440
Hazamada: How dare
you speak to me that way?!

307
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:25,810
Ow! That hurt!

308
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,510
Show off: Punching a guy
made of wood

309
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:28,740
was bound to end badly.

310
00:13:28,780 --> 00:13:30,380
That was pretty stupid of you.

311
00:13:30,410 --> 00:13:32,480
Hazamada: Shut the hell up,
and quit crowdin’ me!

312
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:35,950
Damn it. He’s really
starting to get to me.

313
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:38,450
This always happens
with my stand.

314
00:13:38,490 --> 00:13:41,290
Like when I copied my crush,
junko, the other day,

315
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,730
