into a complete bitch.

316
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:46,800
I couldn’t take it,
so the entire thing was a flop.

317
00:13:46,830 --> 00:13:50,530
Is there no one halfway decent
on this miserable planet?

318
00:13:50,570 --> 00:13:52,800
That damn josuke’ll get his,

319
00:13:52,830 --> 00:13:54,870
but first I have to take care
of jotaro.

320
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:56,810
I’ll crush him into paste.

321
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,240
( Laughs )

322
00:13:58,270 --> 00:13:59,880
This is gonna be good.

323
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:01,580
Man: Huh?

324
00:14:01,610 --> 00:14:03,050
You’ve gotta be kidding!

325
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,910
That guy smudged my motorcycle!

326
00:14:04,950 --> 00:14:06,480
Man #2: What a douche.

327
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:08,520
Man #1: Damn that dumb-ass
and his dirty fingers!

328
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,990
I’m going to kill him!

329
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:12,520
Man #2: Take it easy, man.
It was probably an accident,

330
00:14:12,550 --> 00:14:14,020
you know? Besides...

331
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:16,790
Man #1: What? Do you think
I care if that asshole hears me?

332
00:14:16,830 --> 00:14:18,790
Just look at how he’s walkin’.

333
00:14:18,830 --> 00:14:20,560
Damn, it’s like watching

334
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,830
a dying cricket
on a death march.

335
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:25,800
( Man #2 laughs )
Man, that was a sick burn!

336
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:26,800
Good one, dude!

337
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,000
Man #1: Yeah? You think?

338
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,340
It was pretty funny.

339
00:14:29,370 --> 00:14:31,410
( Men laughing )

340
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,740
( Hazamada growls )

341
00:14:32,770 --> 00:14:34,380
( Man #2 yelps )

342
00:14:36,110 --> 00:14:37,810
( Man #1 gasping )

343
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:39,580
Hazamada: That’s it, show off.

344
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:43,390
Hold him still
while I settle the score.

345
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:45,990
( Man #1 panting ) What the hell
are you doing, you freak?

346
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:48,590
Knock it off! ( Groans )

347
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:50,490
Hazamada: Now don’t worry
your pretty little head

348
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:51,590
about what i’m gonna do.

349
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,400
Just focus on relaxing,

350
00:14:53,430 --> 00:14:56,530
and i’ll make sure
you never open that mouth again.

351
00:14:56,570 --> 00:15:00,440
( Man #1 shudders ) No!

352
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,610
( Hazamada gasps )

353
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:04,440
( Man #1 groans )

354
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:06,580
Hazamada: A glass shard?

355
00:15:06,610 --> 00:15:10,010
♪

356
00:15:10,050 --> 00:15:11,980
( Koichi panting )

357
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:14,420
( Hazamada gasps )
Josuke higashikata?!

358
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:16,580
What the hell?!
Even the shrimp’s still alive.

359
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:19,020
Koichi: Hazamada!

360
00:15:19,050 --> 00:15:21,620
Josuke: We finally caught up
to you and Pinocchio!

361
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:23,690
Hazamada: How soon we forget.

362
00:15:23,730 --> 00:15:26,800
Come face to face with
my show off if you dare, josuke.

363
00:15:26,830 --> 00:15:28,060
The moment you do,

364
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:30,370
you’ll instantly
be turned into a puppet.

365
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:32,600
Control him! Now, show off!

366
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:33,800
Koichi: Not so fast.

367
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,870
♪

368
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:38,110
( Both gasp )

369
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:40,710
Hazamada: Wh-what’s happening?!

370
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:42,080
Josuke:
You mean it isn’t obvious?

371
00:15:42,110 --> 00:15:43,810
That glass shard
I chucked your way

372
00:15:43,850 --> 00:15:45,550
wasn’t meant to take you out.

373
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:48,920
