reform into its original shape.

374
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:52,490
Show off:
You sliced off my right hand,

375
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:54,820
and it turned back into wood!

376
00:15:54,860 --> 00:15:56,560
This isn’t good, hazamada!

377
00:15:56,590 --> 00:15:58,130
Hazamada: Settle down!

378
00:15:58,160 --> 00:16:00,630
Just pretend you’re resting
your hand in your pocket.

379
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:02,360
No one’s gonna know.

380
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:05,070
More importantly,
that bastard jotaro

381
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:07,740
should arrive at the station
any minute now.

382
00:16:07,770 --> 00:16:10,110
As much as i’d like
to get rid of josuke,

383
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:12,940
we don’t have time to waste
tracking him down.

384
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:16,480
Show off:
H-hazamada, wait for me!

385
00:16:17,510 --> 00:16:18,910
Josuke: I see.

386
00:16:18,950 --> 00:16:21,420
So they’re meeting
in front of the station, huh?

387
00:16:21,450 --> 00:16:22,850
Koichi: We have to get moving.

388
00:16:22,890 --> 00:16:24,720
Those two
already have a head start,

389
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:26,920
not to mention the fact
that the road they just took

390
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,820
is the fastest way
to get to the station.

391
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:30,930
Josuke: Yeah,
you’re probably right,

392
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:34,130
but i’ve got a secret weapon
in tow, koichi.

393
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,730
Koichi: You do?

394
00:16:37,530 --> 00:16:39,540
♪

395
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:42,600
Jotaro: So he’s not here yet.

396
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:44,040
I guess
he ran into some trouble.

397
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:46,070
Hazamada: What’s the word?

398
00:16:46,110 --> 00:16:47,880
You see josuke anywhere?

399
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,510
Show off: Nope,
nowhere to be found.

400
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:51,650
There’s nothing
to worry about, though.

401
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,150
If I so much
as glance at him,

402
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:55,650
he’ll be turned
into my puppet in a flash.

403
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:56,750
( Chime beeping )

404
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:57,790
Hazamada: Huh?

405
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,990
Show off:
Hear that, hazamada?

406
00:16:59,020 --> 00:17:00,760
A train’s coming.

407
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:03,430
( Hazamada groans )
It’s the crossing from hell.

408
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:04,890
Waiting’ll cost valuable time,

409
00:17:04,930 --> 00:17:06,860
so let’s
cut through the station!

410
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:10,470
( Laughs )

411
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:12,500
Even if he catches up to us,

412
00:17:12,530 --> 00:17:14,700
the train’ll stop him!
Take that!

413
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:16,040
Show off:
There’s one minute left,

414
00:17:16,070 --> 00:17:17,610
and all signs point to us

415
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:19,210
making it
to the meeting spot first.

416
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,210
( Hazamada laughs )

417
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,610
I win!

418
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,210
Huh? What the...

419
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:28,520
( Gasps ) Look there!

420
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:30,550
It’s josuke
and that brat, koichi.

421
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:32,790
( Growls )
Why’s the crossing open?!

422
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,820
Will someone explain
what the hell’s going on?!

423
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:36,690
Show off: Hazamada, over there!

424
00:17:36,730 --> 00:17:38,660
Hazamada: Damn it!
He tricked us!

425
00:17:38,690 --> 00:17:41,060
What is that stand?!

426
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:43,870
( Chime beeping )

427
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:47,000
Josuke: Great, right? You make
the perfect secret weapon.

428
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:49,200
Thanks for the assist
back there, koichi.

429
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,870
( Koichi chuckles )

430
00:17:50,910 --> 00:17:52,880
( Running footsteps )

431
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:54,580
Josuke: There he is!

432
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:58,150
Hey, jotaro, it’s me!
It’s josuke!

433
00:17:58,180 --> 00:17:59,550
Jotaro: Huh? Hey.

434
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:00,920
Koichi: We made it in time!

435
00:18:00,950 --> 00:18:04,750
Boy, we got hazamada good,
didn’t we, josuke?

436
00:18:04,790 --> 00:18:06,120
Jotaro: Did something happen?

437
00:18:06,150 --> 00:18:08,090
( No audible dialogue )

438
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:10,130
♪

439
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,930
( Hazamada growls )

440
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:14,930
Jotaro: A copy?

441
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:16,730
A stand that copied
your likeness

442
00:18:16,770 --> 00:18:17,900
down to the fingerprints?

443
00:18:17,930 --> 00:18:19,540
Josuke: Yeah, it’s crazy, right?

444
00:18:19,570 --> 00:18:21,600
If he’d gotten to you
before me and koichi,

445
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,970
who knows
what would have happened?

446
00:18:23,010 --> 00:18:25,140
Koichi: But at least
now we can relax a bit.

447
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:26,570
Josuke:
I severed its right hand,

448
00:18:26,610 --> 00:18:28,580
so it ought to be easy
to tell us apart.

449
00:18:28,610 --> 00:18:31,280
I had to think on my feet,
but figured that would be best.

450
00:18:31,310 --> 00:18:34,150
- Now we play the waiting game.
- Jotaro: Got it.

451
00:18:34,180 --> 00:18:35,550
Koichi: We weren’t
that far ahead,

452
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:36,890
so they should show up
pretty soon.

453
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:37,890
Jotaro: Right.

454
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,960
Josuke: Hmm? Huh?

455
00:18:39,990 --> 00:18:41,960
What am I doing with this?

456
00:18:41,990 --> 00:18:43,730
This doesn’t make sense.

457
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:47,300
Why would I take a pen
out of jotaro’s pocket?

458
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:51,130
( Gasps ) I-I can’t move.

459
00:18:51,170 --> 00:18:53,640
It’s like my arm
is frozen in place.

460
00:18:53,670 --> 00:18:54,870
( Gasps )

461
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:02,540
- ( Show off chuckles )
- ( Josuke gasps )

462
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,980
- ( Show off chuckles )
- ( Josuke chuckles )

463
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:06,210
- ( Show off stammers )
- ( Josuke stammers )

464
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:09,050
Wait.
The other side of the glass.

465
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:11,090
Shit. It’s him.

466
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:15,120
- ( Pen clicks )
- ( Josuke grunting )

467
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:18,090
Hazamada: Josuke higashikata...

468
00:19:18,130 --> 00:19:19,760
Like it or not,

469
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:22,330
you’re gonna plunge that pen
into jotaro’s brain.

470
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:25,200
The blunt-force trauma
should kill him instantly.

471
00:19:25,230 --> 00:19:27,900
After all, leaving him alive
isn’t really an option now,

472
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:30,910
