would only heal him anyway.

473
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:31,970
( Growls )

474
00:19:32,010 --> 00:19:33,280
It’s your fault!

475
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:35,810
Your meddling is
the cause of this, josuke!

476
00:19:35,840 --> 00:19:38,880
I was only gonna beat jotaro up
and chase him out of town

477
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:41,850
before you involved yourself
in my business!

478
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:46,190
But now jotaro’s gonna die,
and it’ll be by your hand.

479
00:19:46,220 --> 00:19:48,220
Live with that,
you uppity ass-hat!

480
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:50,660
( Josuke grunting )

481
00:19:50,690 --> 00:19:52,660
♪

482
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:56,070
Do it!

483
00:19:56,100 --> 00:20:00,100
Send him to hell, show off!

484
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:02,100
Josuke: J-jotaro.

485
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:04,310
- Man #1: Bastard!
- ( Hazamada gags )

486
00:20:04,340 --> 00:20:05,940
- Josuke: Huh?
- Jotaro: Huh?

487
00:20:05,970 --> 00:20:08,010
Is something the matter, josuke?

488
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:10,210
Josuke: Uh, no,

489
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,980
though, fortunately for me,

490
00:20:12,010 --> 00:20:15,920
it looks like those biker dudes
finally tracked down hazamada.

491
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:17,850
- ( Wood creaks )
- ( Hazamada gasps )

492
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:19,690
Man #1: You’re just
where josuke said you’d be,

493
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,090
you piece of bug shit,

494
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:23,260
hiding out at the station
like the coward you are!

